title: Kiss Woman Woman Light Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone
description: Depicts two women kissing, one with a light skin tone and the other with a medium skin tone. Represents romantic love and affection between women.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts two women leaning in for a tender kiss, rendered with Apple's signature soft, rounded edges and a gentle 3D sheen. The light and medium skin tones are subtly shaded with realistic lighting, conveying warmth and affection. This representation of a loving embrace is a beautiful way to express romance and deep connection within messages on Apple devices.
